    "body" : "<p>All the constants of an enum type can be obtained by calling the implicit <code>public static T[] values()</code> method of that type:</p>\n\n<pre><code> for (Direction d : Direction.values()) {\n     System.out.println(d);\n }\n</code></pre>\n"
