      "body" : "@jacktrades: It is an implicit method that exists only in the compiler. Therefore the base class can not declare a method with the same name and thus it does not get included in the automatically generated Javadocs.  <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se7/html/jls-8.html#jls-8.9.2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se7/html/jls-8.html#jls-8.9&zwnj;&#8203;.2</a>"
