      "comment_id" : 67954492,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "From the <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/EnumSet.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">documentation for <code>EnumSet</code></a>: <i>The iterator returned by the iterator method traverses the elements in their <b>natural order</b> (the order in which the enum constants are declared)</i>.  This guarantees that the order of iteration matches the order returned by <code>Enum.values()</code>."
    } ],
